Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 20/08/2023
This policy describes how TOJ GAMES LLC ("we", "our", or "us") processes the personal information we collect about you when you use our products and services. By using our Services, you agree to this policy.
1. Information We Collect
The information we collect depends on what Services you use and how you use them.
1.1 Information You Provide:
Account Information:
We collect your email, username, and password when you create an account.
Contact Information:
We collect your name, email, and any other details you provide when contacting us.
Payment Information:
Payment details for in-app purchases are processed by third-party providers, not stored by us.
1.2 Information Collected Automatically:
Device Information:
We collect data about your device, including hardware, operating system, IP address, and unique identifiers.
Usage Information:
We collect data on how you interact with our Services, such as pages viewed and gameplay activity.
Location Information:
We may collect location data from your device settings or IP address.
1.3 Information from Third Parties:
We may receive information from third-party services, such as social media platforms, if you link your account with them.
2. How We Use Your Information
We use your information for the following purposes:
Service Provision and Improvement:
To operate, maintain, and enhance our Services.
Communication:
To respond to inquiries, send updates, and provide customer support.
Payment Processing:
To manage transactions for in-app purchases or subscriptions.
Personalization:
To tailor your experience with personalized content and recommendations.
Security:
To protect our Services and prevent fraud or illegal activities.
Legal Compliance:
To meet legal obligations and respond to legal requests.
3. How We Share Your Information
We may share your information with:
Service Providers:
Third-party vendors who help us operate our Services, such as payment processors, hosting services, and customer support providers.
Legal Authorities:
If required by law or to protect our legal rights.
Business Transfers:
If our business undergoes a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets.
With Your Consent:
When you agree to share your information with third parties.
4. Third-Party Services
Our Services use third-party services, such as payment processors, analytics tools, and ad networks, which may collect and manage your data according to their own privacy policies. Below are some of the third-party services we use:
Google Play Services
Google AdMob
Google Analytics for Firebase
Firebase Crashlytics
Unity
Xsolla
Please review the privacy policies of these third-party providers for more information.
5. App Permissions
Our app may request permissions to function properly. These may include:
Location Access:
For location-based services.
Microphone Access:
For in-game voice chat or recording features.
Storage Access:
To store game data or user-generated content.
You can manage these permissions in your device settings.
6. Push Notifications
With your consent, we may send push notifications to your device for updates and information related to our Services. You can opt-out by adjusting your device settings.
7. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information. However, no data transmission or storage system can be guaranteed to be completely secure.
8. Children's Privacy
Our Services are not mainly intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we discover that such information has been collected, we will take steps to delete it.
9. Links to Other Sites
Our Services may contain links to third-party websites or services that are not operated by us. If you click on a third-party link, you will be directed to that third party's site. We recommend reviewing the privacy policy of any third-party site you visit, as we are not responsible for their practices.
10. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make significant changes, we will notify you by posting a notice on our website or by other means. Continued use of our Services after any changes indicates your agreement with the updated policy.
11. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
support@tojgames.com
